ec7m bu\u1ed3n v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp</span> do l\u1ed7i ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 40 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/ong-ta-la-ke-giet-nguoi-mau-lanh-ke-khong-co-trai-tim-184-184070.html\" target=\"_blank\">tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Michael Oliver l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebb gi\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1eddi</span>. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi g\u00f3c nh\u00ecn c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t chuy\u00ean gia, c\u1ef1u tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng Graham Poll l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 v\u1eady.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Benatia ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi Lucas Vazquez, t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Oliver l\u00e0 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 s\u1edf. Graham Poll cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Anh \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1ea5t ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7y m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ngo\u00e0i ra, anh \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb bao v\u00e2y b\u1edfi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Juventus, nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh \u0111\u1ec3 ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. Buffon nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf v\u00ec l\u1ed7i ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng qu\u00e1 quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Michael Oliver th\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1t Benatia (s\u1ed1 4)\" title=\"Michael Oliver th\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1t Benatia (s\u1ed1 4)\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/quyet-dinh-tang-penalty-cho-real-madrid-la-chinh-xac.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Michael Oliver th\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1t Benatia (s\u1ed1 4)</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00f4i t\u1eebng n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 can \u0111\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ec3 ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, v\u00e0 HLV Arsene Wenger cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi r\u00e1c r\u01b0\u1edfi. Tuy nhi\u00ean sau khi xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u00f4ng \u1ea5y s\u1ebd hi\u1ec3u l\u1eddi t\u00f4i n\u00f3i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Th\u1eadt ti\u1ebfc khi FA (Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh) kh\u00f4ng th\u0103ng c\u1ea5p s\u1edbm h\u01a1n cho tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Michael Oliver. Anh \u1ea5y \u0111\u1ee7 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u00e0 ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018&rdquo; &ndash; Graham Poll k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, &ldquo;n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n&rdquo; tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a Oliver &ndash; trung v\u1ec7 Mehdi Benatia cay \u0111\u1eafng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u: &ldquo;T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 cam \u0111oan r\u1eb1ng, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea9y Lucas Vazquez. C\u1eadu ta l\u0103n ra s\u00e2n v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m g\u00ec kh\u00e1c trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110\u01b0a ra m\u1ed9t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n v\u00e0o ph\u00fat 93 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u v\u00f4 l\u00fd. B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u1ee7y ho\u1ea1i gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m g\u00ec \u0111\u00e2y?&rdquo; &ndash; Benatia cho bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 Real Madrid 1-3 Juventus<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/14088661/013100\" rel=\"nofollow\">Real vs Juve</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft li\u00ean quan sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/ong-ta-la-ke-giet-nguoi-mau-lanh-ke-khong-co-trai-tim-184-184070.html\">\u00d4ng ta l\u00e0 k\u1ebb gi\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u00e1u l\u1ea1nh, k\u1ebb kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 tr\u00e1i tim</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/buffon-va-ky-niem-buon-trong-tran-cuoi-cung-tai-champions-league-184-184069.html\">Buffon v\u00e0 k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m bu\u1ed3n trong tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i Champions League</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/buffon-juventus-xung-dang-nhan-duoc-nhung-loi-khen-ngoi-184-184066.html\">Buffon: Juventus x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/zidane-kich-ban-tai-bernabeu-nam-ngoai-suc-tuong-tuong-cua-toi-184-184065.html\">Zidane: K\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i Bernabeu n\u1eb1m ngo\u00e0i s\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/du-am-real-13-juventus-hut-chet-tren-san-nha-184-184064.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Real 1-3 Juventus: H\u00fat ch\u1ebft tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/thong-ke-dang-nho-trong-tran-real-madrid-13-juve-184-184061.html\">Nh\u1eefng c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb trong tr\u1eadn Real Madrid 1-3 Juve</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/thong-ke-khong-the-tin-duoc-ve-ronaldo-sau-tran-dau-voi-juventus-184-184062.html\">Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ec1 Ronaldo sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Juventus?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h</div>\r\n</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1063","checkdouble":"184071"},{"date":"19:08 11/04","title":"MU ch\u1ed1t 2 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau thay Anthony Martial?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/29/mu-chot-2-muc-tieu-thay-anthony-martial.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.