ght:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 \u0111ang nh\u1eafm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Anthony Martial, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean.</strong></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2>Martial c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi M.U \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Anthony Martial \u0111ang ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o M.U. Ch\u1ec9 t\u00ednh ri\u00eang \u1edf Premier League anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 9 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 5 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n, song ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuyen nhuong MU 2018 nham 2 cau thu thay Martial hinh anh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 nh\u1eafm 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thay Martial h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/29/Bao-Phap-khang-dinh-Martial-muon-roi-MU-trong-he-toi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&nbsp;Martial c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi M.U \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Rashford, t\u1eeb khi Alexis Sanchez \u0111\u1ebfn Old Trafford anh l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh m\u1edbi. Trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y Mourinho th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Sanchez \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 bu\u1ed9c Martial ph\u1ea3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n, anh \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ednh chuy\u1ec7n ra \u0111i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n. Hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-chi-80-trieu-bang-mua-tien-dao-anthony-martial-180-173928.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Real ng\u1ecf \u00fd mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Martial</strong></span>, PSG c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. BL\u0110 M.U mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u1edf l\u1ea1i, song h\u1ecd c\u0169ng chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n n\u1ebfu anh ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>2 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u thay Martial</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 \u0111ang nh\u1eafm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Anthony Martial, Mourinho \u0111ang nh\u1eafm Gareth Bale c\u1ee7a Real Madrid v\u00e0 Willian c\u1ee7a Chelsea nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gareth Bale cua Real\" title=\"Gareth Bale cua Real\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/1/hlv-zinedine-zidane-phat-bieu-ve-gareth-bale.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 nh\u1eafm Gareth Bale thay Martial</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/gareth-bale-44960.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Bale </strong></span>\u0111ang kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Real Madrid, anh th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Bernabeu. Vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Isco, Lucas Vasquez v\u00e0 Marco Asensio khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn s\u1ee9c \u00e9p r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, anh mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Willian, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil t\u1eebng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Mourinho \u1edf Chelsea, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 Old Trafford.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Real b\u00e1n Bale, chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. C\u00f2n v\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Willian, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Martial \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/191176-40942/033100\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Martial \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1062","checkdouble":"184046"},{"date":"19:39 11/04","title":"\"Liverpool c\u1ea7n 4 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0o m\u00f9a t\u1edbi\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/11/liverpool-can-4-ban-hop-dong-chat-luong-de-thanh-cong-vao-mua-toi.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;marg