in-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>C\u1ef1u sao tuy\u1ec3n Anh, Chris Waddle cho r\u1eb1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Liverpool 2018 c\u1ea7n th\u00eam \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 4 t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</strong></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</h2>\r\n<h2>Liverpool chi ti\u00eau m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong nh\u1eefng k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/liverpool-2.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Liverpool </strong></span>lu\u00f4n chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao. H\u00e8 2016, h\u1ecd b\u1ecf ra h\u01a1n 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Mane.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuyen nhuong Liverpool 2018 mua 4 sao khung hinh anh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Liverpool 2018 mua 4 sao kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/Chuyen-nhuong-Liverpool-2018-mua-4-sao-khung-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Van Dijk v\u00e0 Salah l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh kh\u1ee7ng trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nH\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield chi g\u1ea7n 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Mohamed Salah t\u1eeb Roma v\u00e0 Alex Oxlade-Chamberlain t\u1eeb Arsenal. \u0110\u1ebfn th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m nay h\u1ecd chi 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 trung v\u1ec7 Virgil van Dijk t\u1eeb Southampton.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u00fap ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a The Kop \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. H\u1ecd \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League v\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong Top 3 \u1edf Premier League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool c\u1ea7n b\u1ed5 sung \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u01a1n</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ef1u sao tuy\u1ec3n Anh, Chris Waddle cho r\u1eb1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Liverpool 2018 c\u1ea7n th\u00eam \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 4 t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Paulo Dybala cua Juventus\" title=\"Paulo Dybala cua Juventus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/26/atletico-mua-paulo-dybala-cung-real-va-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Liverpool 2018 quan t\u00e2m Paulo Dybala\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u201cLiverpool k\u00e9m Man City \u0111\u1ebfn 17 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf Premier League, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch\u00a0ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Liverpool v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n b\u1ed5 sung l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201c\u1ede Premier League c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, b\u1edfi v\u1eady b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Liverpool, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n th\u00eam 4 ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u00e0y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Klopp kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Liverpool s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay Coutinho. Liverpool thu v\u1ec1 160 tri\u1ec7u euro t\u1eeb ti\u1ec1n b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil, nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a d\u00f9ng t\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111ang nh\u1eafm m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau thay Coutinho. Mirror \u0111\u01b0a tin, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/liverpool-chi-110-trieu-bang-cho-nguoi-thay-the-coutinho-172-183803.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Liverpool quan t\u00e2m Dybala c\u1ee7a Juventus</strong></span>, song h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 110 tri\u1ec7u euro cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 Mahrez, Malcom hay Manuel Lanzini c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Klopp nh\u1eafm thay ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1061","checkdouble":"184050"},{"date":"19:49 11/04","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! \u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1i \u01b0u c\u1ee7a Tottenham tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/11/day-doi-hinh-toi-uu-cua-tottenham-truoc-man-city.png","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid