);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ef1u HLV Chelsea l\u00e0 Avram Grant cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ebd Chelsea n\u00ean gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i Diego Costa. Th\u00e0nh t\u00edch y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m c\u1ee7a The Blues \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay c\u00f3 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c thi\u1ebfu \u0111i m\u1ed9t trung phong t\u1ea7m c\u1ee1 nh\u01b0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</h2>\r\n<h2>N\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a Conte</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Diego Costa b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 t\u1ea1i Brazil. S\u1edf d\u0129 anh \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y l\u00e0 b\u1edfi HLV Conte \u0111\u00e3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o b\u1eb1ng tin nh\u1eafn r\u1eb1ng anh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 n\u00ean ra \u0111i. \u0110\u1ebfn th\u00e1ng M\u1ed9t, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/diego-costa-chinh-thuc-tro-ve-atletico-madrid-180-176636.html\" target=\"_blank\">Costa \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho ph\u00e9p ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t vi\u1ec7c chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Atletico Madrid</span> v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng 57 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, c\u1ef1u HLV Avram Grant cho r\u1eb1ng Chelsea \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ebd ra n\u00ean n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u01a1n trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Diego Costa. Theo \u00f4ng, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a The Blues hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u00f3 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n l\u1edbn v\u00ec s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cB\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p nh\u01b0 Diego Costa ra \u0111i d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. Kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 s\u1ebd \u1ed5n khi m\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Ng\u00e0y nay, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi h\u1ecd. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Chelsea kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay l\u00e0 v\u00ec h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t Diego Costa kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Avram Grant Dang le Chelsea nen giu lai Diego Costa hinh anh\" title=\"HLV Avram Grant \u0110\u00e1ng l\u1ebd Chelsea n\u00ean gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i Diego Costa h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/6/dang-le-chelsea-nen-giu-lai-diego-costa.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV\u00a0Avram Grant cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ebd Chelsea n\u00ean gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i Diego Costa</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai gian kh\u00f3 ch\u1edd Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng theo HLV Avram Grant, Chelsea kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng thu h\u00fat \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi khi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i Champions League \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng c\u0169ng tin t\u01b0\u1edfng The Blues c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1eady sau n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cD\u0129 nhi\u00ean vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 Champions League c\u00f3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi h\u1ecd. B\u1edfi v\u00ec nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 Champions League. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean h\u1ecd l\u00e2m v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u00f3.</em><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-phap/tan-hlv-cua-psg-muon-rut-ruot-chelsea-197-184021.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/19/tan-hlv-cua-psg-muon-rut-ruot-chelsea.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-phap/tan-hlv-cua-psg-muon-rut-ruot-chelsea-197-184021.html\">T\u00e2n HLV c\u1ee7a PSG mu\u1ed1n r\u00fat ru\u1ed9t Chelsea?</span><br>\r\n<span>PSG mua NGolo Kante, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a Thomas Tuchel, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n l\u00e0 t\u00e2n HLV c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<em><br>\r\n\u201cH\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o nh\u00f3m d\u1ef1 Champions League c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 n\u0103m. V\u00e0 k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 n\u0103m m\u00e0 h\u1ecd v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 x\u1ebfp \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 6 t\u1ea1i Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Chelsea m\u1ea5t su\u1ea5t d\u1ef1 Champions League. Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u1ecd s\u1ebd b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n n\u00e0y. Cho \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd, m\u1ed7i khi Chelsea c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i, h\u1ecd th\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sau \u0111\u00f3\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tin t\u1ee9c li\u00ean quan t\u1edbi CLB\u00a0Chelsea:</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-toi-1104-mu-chi-so-tien-khung-mua-hang-thai-chelsea-184-184049.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 11/04: M.U chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u1ee7ng mua h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-va-psg-tranh-gianh-kenedy-172-184027.html\">Arsenal v\u00e0 PSG tranh gi\u00e0nh h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-phap/tan-hlv-cua-psg-muon-rut-ruot-chelsea-197-184021.html\">T\u00e2n HLV c\u1ee7a PSG mu\u1ed1n r\u00fat ru\u1ed9t Chelsea?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/lam-nen-ky-tich-sao-roma-tien-the-xat-muoi-noi-dau-chelsea-184-183987.html\">L\u00e0m n\u00ean k\u1ef3 t\u00edch, sao Roma ti\u1ec7n th\u1ec3 x\u00e1t mu\u1ed1i n\u1ed7i \u0111au Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-kho-lot-top-4-hazard-van-lac-quan-172-183939.html\">Chelsea kh\u00f3 v\u00e0o top 4, Hazard v\u1eabn l\u1ea1c quan</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-sa-thai-conte-nhung-lai-tu-choi-den-bu-9-trieu-bang-172-183929.html\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n sa th\u1ea3i Conte nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec1n b\u00f9 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (Bongda24h)</strong></div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1058","checkdouble":"184060"},{"date":"15:54 11/04","title":"Ph\u00eda HAGL ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i g\u00ec sau khi b\u1ea7u T\u00fa \u1edf l\u1ea1i VPF","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/24/truong-doan-hagl-bau-duc-chua-chi-dao-rut-khoi-vleague.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate>a:hover{color:#f00;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}.articlerelate2{padding:6px;min-height:72px}div.articlerelate2>a{color:#000;text-d