us:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>CLB th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Italia v\u1eeba t\u1ea1o ra c\u01a1n \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n khi lo\u1ea1i Barca kh\u1ecfi Champions League. Ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch James Pallotta tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 Roma kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Alisson.</strong></h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool v\u00e0 AS Roma l\u00e0 2 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Cup C1, tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft di\u1ec5n ra. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, 2 &ldquo;g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3&rdquo; Barca v\u00e0 Man City \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1ch vali v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Qu\u00e1 vui m\u1eebng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi AS Roma tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Alisson Becker. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Liverpool, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 Roma ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea1m m\u1eb7t \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, v\u00e0 t\u00ednh c\u1ea3 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, Alisson \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh. Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, v\u00e0 \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Liverpool \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Roma kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Alisson m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y\" title=\"Roma kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Alisson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/vua-de-bep-barca-nguoi-roma-tiep-tuc-dem-tin-buon-cho-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Roma kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Alisson m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00e0i Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch James Pallotta cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i y\u00eau c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u00e0 t\u1ea1i sao Alisson l\u1ea1i ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i ch\u1ee9? C\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i, v\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y kia m\u00e0. T\u00f4i ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Alisson, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n m\u00f9a n\u00e0y ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf c\u1eadu \u1ea5y gi\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c n\u00e0o.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Alisson n\u0103m nay 24 tu\u1ed5i, v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stadio Olimpico. \u0110\u1ec3 so s\u00e1nh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Brazil. T\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 Ederson Moraes &ndash; ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Man City.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Liverpool, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League nh\u01b0 Roma &ndash; v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng Loris Karius. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Jurgen Klopp c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed5 sung l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, v\u00e0 \u0111ang nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi Alisson v\u00e0 Jan Oblak c\u1ee7a Atletico.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f2n \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi CLB th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Italia, Roma kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Alisson l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, sau khi h\u1ecd m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m \u1edf th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Mohamed Salah khi c\u0169ng b\u00e1n cho Liverpool v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 r\u1ebb m\u1ea1t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/nhung-dieu-se-xay-ra-sau-tham-bai-lich-su-cua-barca-184-184014.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/11/nhung-dieu-se-xay-ra-sau-tham-bai-lich-su-cua-barca.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/nhung-dieu-se-xay-ra-sau-tham-bai-lich-su-cua-barca-184-184014.html\">4