nd-position:-64px -224px}.ui-icon-grip-diagonal-se{background-position:-80px -224px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-top,.ui-corner-left,.ui-corner-tl{border-top-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-top,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-tr{border-top-right-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-left,.ui-corner-bl{border-bottom-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ec7nh gi\u1eefa 2 CLB k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch t\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha, khi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00e0y l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ebb kh\u00e1c. M\u1ed9t s\u00e2n kh\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1ng s\u1eb5n cho CR7, trong tr\u1eadn Real Madrid vs Juventus t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.</strong></h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0o \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i Champions League n\u0103m nay, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 trong c\u1ea3 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed d\u00e0i c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 &ndash; c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0 k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh nh\u01b0 Ronaldo &ndash; Messi. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ngo\u00e0i h\u00e0nh tinh, to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao kh\u00e1c ch\u1ec9 ng\u1ed3i &ldquo;chi\u1ebfu d\u01b0\u1edbi&rdquo;. Nh\u01b0 Neymar gi\u1edd ch\u1ec9 m\u01a1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd 2 ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n nhau \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t &ndash; tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League Si\u00eau kinh \u0111i\u1ec3n, v\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 k\u1ec3 h\u1ebft. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, hi\u1ebfm c\u00f3 khi n\u00e0o 2 ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n n\u1ea3y l\u1eeda nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Truoc tran Real Madrid vs Juventus Thoi khac cua Ronaldo hinh anh\" title=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Real Madrid vs Juventus Th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc c\u1ee7a Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/rona.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng gi\u00e1p m\u1eb7t \u1edf chung k\u1ebft C1</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00e0y lu\u00f4n \u0111i c\u00f9ng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ebb kh\u00e1c. V\u00e0 th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Cris Ronaldo, khi Leo Messi m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 thua th\u1ea3m t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League. \u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 CR7 chi\u1ebfm l\u1ea5y v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cao nh\u1ea5t, khi k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Barca \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi gi\u1edd, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi\u1ebfu \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh khi \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf La Liga. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Leo Messi b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 d\u1eef d\u1ed9i, c\u00f9ng Barca th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00fa \u0103n ba v\u00e0 tr\u00e0n tr\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00f2i l\u1ea1i Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng. Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, Messi \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh cao, khi ch\u1eb3ng ai tin anh b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi h\u01a1n c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha (25 b\u00e0n/ 15 tr\u1eadn), nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Ronaldo s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0103n m\u1eebng ng\u1ea1o ngh\u1ec5 khi ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi Buffon \u0111\u00eam nay. 6 cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi Juve, anh ghi 9 b\u00e0n, v\u00e0 ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 l\u00fd g\u00ec Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u00e2n kh\u1ea5u, v\u00ec v\u1eady \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1ng s\u1eb5n cho Ronaldo v\u00e0 Real Madrid, khi K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e1i k\u1ebft qu\u00e1 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u1edbi CR7, khi anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ecbp &ldquo;c\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0o m\u1eb7t&rdquo; Leo Messi &ndash; ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi b\u1ecb Roma \u0111\u00e1 bay kh\u1ecfi Cup C1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\"><br>\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo\" title=\"Ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/4/barzagli-tam-phuc-khau-phuc-ban-thang-cua-ronaldo-se-di-vao-lich-su.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo \u0111ang th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tin n\u1ed5i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1eebng d\u1eabm v\u00e0o v\u1ebft xe \u0111\u1ed5</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">2 ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y lu\u00f4n song h\u00e0nh trong danh s\u00e1ch r\u00fat g\u1ecdn Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng, th\u1ef1c ra c\u00f3 s\u1ed1 ph\u1eadn r\u1ea5t t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i h\u00f4m nay c\u1ee7a Messi ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Ronaldo, ngay ng\u00e0y mai. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Argentina \u0111\u00e3 ng\u00e3 g\u1ee5c, nh\u01b0ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 Ronaldo c\u00f3 n\u1eafm b\u1eaft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i hay kh\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 lo\u1ea1i Barca l\u00e0 ai? AS Roma, m\u1ed9t CLB c\u1ee7a \u00dd. Ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay, truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf m\u1ef3 \u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e3 &ldquo;n\u00e1o lo\u1ea1n&rdquo; v\u1ec1 c\u00fa l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng kinh \u0111i\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a Roma. H\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111em l\u1ea1i ngu\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 Juventus b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfp. C\u00f9ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 3 b\u00e0n, n\u1ebfu Roma l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, c\u1edb g\u00ec Juve l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca tham bai truoc doi bong thu do Italia\" title=\"Barca th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Italia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/nhung-dieu-se-xay-ra-sau-tham-bai-lich-su-cua-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Messi v\u00e0 Barca th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Italia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nAi tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barca h\u00f9ng m\u1ea1nh l\u1ea1i d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng b\u1ecb \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eady, khi h\u1ecd s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi? Nh\u1eefng Messi, Suarez ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ecbp th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, th\u00ec h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Roma c\u00e0y n\u00e1t. C\u1ed9ng th\u00eam nh\u1eefng kinh nghi\u1ec7m h\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eeb th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, Juve ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nghi\u1ec1n n\u00e1t Real Madrid. Ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u1eafc nghi\u1ec7t nh\u01b0 Champions League.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man City c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u00ed d\u1ee5 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, khi \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n Pep Guardiola \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 1 trong 2 \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch (c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Barca). Nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd c\u0169ng th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool c\u1ea3 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn, d\u00f9 v\u1eabn th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong c\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u quen thu\u1ed9c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft, l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf 3 b\u00e0n d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3, phong \u0111\u1ed9 l\u1eabn t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec1u v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0 th\u00e0nh Turin. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, s\u1ef1 s\u01a1 x\u1ea3y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1ebft ch\u1ebft nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1. M\u1ed9t si\u00eau sao nh\u01b0 Leo Messi \u0111\u00e3 s\u1ee5p b\u1eaby, l\u00fd n\u00e0o Ronaldo v\u00e0 Real kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo toa sang truoc Juventus va su ghen ti Messi\" title=\"Ronaldo toa sang truoc Juventus va su ghen ti Messi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/4/ronaldo-toa-sang-tran-dau-juventus-vs-real-madrid-va-su-kho-chiu-cua-messi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>S\u00e2n kh\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1ng s\u1eb5n cho CR7 trong tr\u1eadn Real Madrid vs Juventus</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 l\u1ebd sau tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u01a1 m\u1ed9ng nh\u1ea5t c\u0169ng \u0111\u1eb7t c\u1eeda Real \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 di\u1ec7u mang t\u00ean Roma \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafp l\u1ea1i hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t cho L\u00e3o b\u00e0. Cho d\u00f9 thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng Paulo Dybala ch\u0103ng n\u1eefa, nh\u01b0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u00f4n th\u1ec3 thao t\u1eadp th\u1ec3, c\u00f2n Juve v\u1eabn c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">2 v\u00ed d\u1ee5 cho Real Madrid vs Juventus nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp. Nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u1ecdn l\u1ea5y b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc n\u00e0o, thua nh\u1ee5c nh\u01b0 Barca/ hay ki\u00eau h\u00e3nh nh\u01b0 AS Roma? H\u00e3y \u0111\u00f3n ch\u1edd v\u00e0o l\u00fac 1h45 \u0111\u00eam nay, khi c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi r\u1ed9n r\u00e0ng v\u1edbi ti\u1ebfng nh\u1ea1c Champions League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/cac-cdv-se-yeu-quy-ronaldo-nhu-di-stefano-184-184024.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/5/cac-cdv-se-yeu-quy-ronaldo-nhu-di-stefano.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/cac-cdv-se-yeu-quy-ronaldo-nhu-di-stefano-184-184024.html\">C\u00e1c C\u0110V s\u1ebd y\u00eau qu\u00fd Ronaldo nh\u01b0 Di Stefano</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi Juventus, Ronaldo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Di Stefano &ndash; huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Real Madrid.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/real-madrid-vs-juventus-01h45-ngay-124-cop-chet-de-da-184-183999.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/11/real-madrid-vs-juventus-01h45-ngay-124-cop-chet-de-da.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/real-madrid-vs-juventus-01h45-ngay-124-cop-chet-de-da-184-183999.html\">Real Madrid vs Juventus (01h45 ng\u00e0y 12/4): C\u1ecdp ch\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 da</span><br>\r\nPhong \u0111\u1ed9 ghi b\u00e0n tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Ronaldo ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i, v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp di\u1ec5n trong tr\u1eadn Real Madrid vs Juventus v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i,...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1051","checkdouble":"184040"},{"date":"17:03 11/04","title":"Arsenal v\u00e0 PSG tranh gi\u00e0nh \"h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\" Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/9/20/arsenal-va-psg-tranh-gianh-kenedy.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-wei