web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb ESPN, Arsenal v\u00e0 PSG tranh gi\u00e0nh Kenedy, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i Chelsea. Ph\u00eda The Blues c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 sao tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil ra \u0111i \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</h2>\r\n<h2>Chelsea th\u1ea3i h\u1ed3i Kenedy</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/tieu-hulk-chinh-thuc-tro-thanh-tan-binh-thu-8-cua-chelsea-172-117085.html\" target=\"_blank\">Kenedy gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea</span> t\u1eeb Fluminense v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2015 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 ch\u1ec9 6 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1eeb HLV Jose Mourinho. Nh\u01b0ng khi Guus Hiddink l\u00ean n\u1eafm quy\u1ec1n, Kenedy \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, Kenedy \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge. \u1ede chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ebfn Trung Qu\u1ed1c, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 d\u00ednh ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t scandal v\u1ea1 mi\u1ec7ng v\u00e0 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Chelsea ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-chinh-thuc-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-hau-ve-emerson-palmieri-172-179090.html\" target=\"_blank\">t\u00e2n binh Emerson Palmieri</span> h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng M\u1ed9t c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn cho c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Kenedy gi\u1ea3m \u0111i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i gia nh\u1eadp Newcastle theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. V\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n theo chi\u1ec1u h\u01b0\u1edbng x\u1ea5u, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cao Kenedy kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal va PSG tranh gianh Kenedy hinh anh\" title=\"Arsenal v\u00e0 PSG tranh gi\u00e0nh Kenedy h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/Arsenal-va-PSG-tranh-gianh-Kenedy-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Arsenal v\u00e0 PSG tranh gi\u00e0nh Kenedy</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Ch\u00e2n tr\u1eddi m\u1edbi ch\u1edd sao tr\u1ebb Brazil</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng sau khi r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Chelsea, s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Kenedy b\u1ed7ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean s\u00e1ng s\u1ee7a h\u01a1n t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i. Anh ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 2 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o ch\u1ec9 sau 8 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf Premier League cho Newcastle. V\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y, Kenedy \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>Bayern Munich, Paris Saint-Germain v\u00e0 Arsenal l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang tr\u00f4ng ch\u1edd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Kenedy. Ch\u01b0a l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eedi t\u1edbi Chelsea nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1u mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt th\u00f4ng tin th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Kenedy.</em><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-sa-thai-conte-nhung-lai-tu-choi-den-bu-9-trieu-bang-172-183929.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/9/chelsea-muon-sa-thai-conte-nhung-lai-tu-choi-den-bu-9-trieu-bang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-sa-thai-conte-nhung-lai-tu-choi-den-bu-9-trieu-bang-172-183929.html\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n sa th\u1ea3i Conte nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec1n b\u00f9 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng?</span><br>\r\n<span>BL\u0110 Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecdp g\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e0n v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai HLV Conte. Theo Daily Mail, Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i Conte v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n chi 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec1n...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Kenedy r\u1ea5t mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Chelsea t\u1edbi h\u1ebft th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u1ea3 Conte v\u00e0 ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Chelsea \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n chia tay c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. </em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m x\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a CLB. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a Kenedy t\u1ea1i Newcastle c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ea9y gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y l\u00ean m\u1ed9t m\u1ee9c ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng li\u00ean quan t\u1edbi Chelsea:<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-phap/tan-hlv-cua-psg-muon-rut-ruot-chelsea-197-184021.html\">T\u00e2n HLV c\u1ee7a PSG mu\u1ed1n r\u00fat ru\u1ed9t Chelsea?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/juventus-mua-alvaro-morata-cua-chelsea-172-183915.html\">Juventus mu\u1ed1n gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u \u201cbom x\u1ecbt\u201d Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/watford-chot-gia-ban-hang-hot-richarlison-172-183879.html\">Watford ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng hot Richarlison</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-moi-cua-chelsea-dang-tim-nha-o-london-172-183798.html\">HLV m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111ang t\u00ecm nh\u00e0 \u1edf London?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-2-nha-cam-quan-duoc-chelsea-dam-phan-thay-conte-172-183719.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! 2 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n thay Conte</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/conte-o-lai-chelsea-mua-giai-toi-172-183710.html\">Conte \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Chelsea</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (Bongda24h)</strong></div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1050","checkdouble":"184027"}]}